### 🗃️ Database Requirements
- Postgres database with `blog_posts` table
- Row Level Security (RLS) enabled for public read access
- Indexes on `published_at` and `slug` for performance

### 🔒 Security Updates
- Uses `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` on server only (never exposed to frontend)
- Uses public `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` on frontend (safe to expose)
- Blog posts are read-only from frontend perspective
- HTML content is admin-controlled via Supabase dashboard

